title: Gross domestic product ( GDP ) in Oman 2024
yAxis: Gross domestic product in billion U.S. dollars
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Gross domestic product in billion U.S. dollars, containing a total of 41 data points.
Overall Gross domestic product in billion U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2007 and 2008.
The highest Gross domestic product in billion U.S. dollars, of value 90.56 was reached at Year 2024
The lowest Gross domestic product in billion U.S. dollars, of value 8.23 was reported at Year 1986
